<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="directly-conj">directly <strong><em>conj</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /də'rektli;dɪ'rektli;daɪ'rektli/    美 /də'rektli;dɪ'rektli;daɪ'rektli/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1-as-soon-as">1.★ <strong>一…(就…) (as soon as)：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Directly the teacher came in everyone was quiet. 
老师一进来大家就安静了。</p></div></div>